2100.m_mMessage:
"※ Crescent Moon
• Only Scroll of Firstborn can be used to perform Herald.
• There is a limit on the number of Herald attempts (as shown). Once all attempts are used, this event will close.
• Lords are guaranteed at least 1 SSR Vassal per certain number of Herald attempts.

※ Spirits
• If a duplicate Vassal is obtained, you will receive the Spirit of that Vassal instead.
• Spirits can be used to perform Spirit Siphon on Vassals, increasing their level cap.

※ Spirit Scraps
• When a Vassal you own has reached its Spirit Siphon limit, or you have enough Spirits for them to reach their Spirit Siphon limit, you will receive Spirit Scraps instead.
• Can be used to redeem items in the Shop - Covenant Shop."

• In the Blue Dawn event, <style=Highlight>if no SSR Vassal is obtained after 59 consecutive Heralds, the next Herald will guarantee an SSR Vassal</style>
• This is a common Herald Event whose pity counter is not shared with other events.

• Herald using Soothing Embrace or Moon Tear.
• Limits for daily Heralds apply, and attempts reset every day.

• Altar of Invocation will be unlocked after Heralding 40 times in the Blue Dawn event.

• SSR Vassals from factions not listed above (e.g., Ancestral) are not affected by Altar of Invocation.
• Note: Altar of Invocation requires 15 Vassals to take effect

※ Fragrant Residue
• Each Herald in the Blue Dawn event will provide 1 Fragrant Residue.
• Can be redeemed for items in the Shop - Echo Shop.

※ Spirits
• If a duplicate Vassal is obtained, you will receive its Spirit instead.
• Spirits are used for Spirit Siphon, which increase a Vassal's Max LV.

※ Spirit Scraps
• When obtaining duplicates of Vassals whose Spirit Siphon is at Max LV., or when you have enough Spirits to reach a Vassal's Spirit Siphon Max LV., you will receive Spirit Scraps instead.
• Can be used to redeem items in Shop - Covenant Shop."

2107.m_mMessage:
"For each Blessing Slot, if the check (roll) passes, a Blessing will be granted. If not, the original Blessing will be removed.
Different Blessing types have different drop rates (listed below).
Each Blessing type has multiple levels (usually 15), each featuring different drop rates.
The same type of Blessing cannot be obtained repeatedly, and Blessings already obtained are excluded from rolls.
The roll formula is as follows: [Listed Rate of a Blessing ÷ (100% - Total Rate of Excluded Blessings)].
For locked Blessings, their level and type won't change during Recast or Refinement."

100100.m_mMessage:
"Dear users, 

Before you officially start the next process of the termination of the game account (the “Account”) for Silver and Blood(the “Game”), we'd like to make the following statements for your attention: after termination of the Account, all data (the “Data” which includes but not limited to the avatars, nicknames, battle histories, heroes, skins and other virtual props or items purchased or acquired in the Game, speeches, regions, chat records in the Game, etc. of all characters in the Account) in the Account will be deleted or anonymized, and the related products and services that have been previously connected to the Account will no longer be available, unless otherwise provided by laws and regulations or this Agreement. Once the Account is terminated, it cannot be restored. Please be careful.

If you decide to terminate your Account after deliberation, please be sure to carefully read and fully understand this Agreement and agree to all the contents hereof. Some important clauses may be bolded, color-marked or otherwise reasonably brought to your attention. This Agreement is jointly concluded by you and VIZTA PTE.LTD. (hereinafter referred to as VIZTA or we/us) as a legally binding instrument. By starting the termination process you shall be deemed to have agreed to and complied with this Agreement entirety.        

1.You acknowledge and agree that upon termination of your Account, there will (may) be consequences including but not limited to the following, which you are solely liable for:

1.1 You will not be able to access the Account, and your in-Game friends will not be able to interact with you in the Game.

1.2 You will no longer be able to retrieve, access, obtain, continue to use, and recall your Data in Game, nor will you have the right to ask us to retrieve the aforementioned Data, including, but not limited to, the following Account information, character information, and database information.

1.3 You are aware that when the Account is terminated, the in-Game property of the Account will also be deleted. Therefore, you are specifically advised to confirm if your in-Game property, or in-Game property associated with the Account has been settled before termination of your Account. Once you terminate the Account, you will be deemed to have voluntarily forfeited any in-Game property that may exist in your Account (including but not limited to any in-Game property that has accrued during your use of the Game and that may accrue in the future) and that we have the right to clear any such in-Game property, you shall be responsible for such risk related to the above clear and you agree that you will not seek recovery or compensation from us for any such in-Game property.
         
The aforesaid in-Game property include but are not limited to: the rights and interests and levels of additional paid membership; all data related to the growth and upgrading of Game characters (including but not limited to experience value, honor value, prestige value, title, etc.); unused in-Game virtual currency, virtual props and other virtual items (such as diamonds, bundles, props, subscriptions, etc.); unexpired services that have been purchased; other in-Game property generated but not used or expected in-Game property in the future, etc.

1.4 Once the Account is terminated, it cannot be recovered. If you log onto the Game again with the same device after termination, a new Account will be generated. If only the character is deleted, the character cannot be recovered once terminated. When you log onto the Game using this device again after deletion, a new character will be created in the original Account if no other characters are available; If there are still characters that have not been deleted in the original Account, no new characters will be generated.

1.5 Once the Account is terminated (referring to the expiration of the Cooling-Off Period), the Terms of Service signed by and between you and us regarding the Game will be terminated (except for those that have been agreed to continue to take effect). However, the termination of such Agreement and Terms of Service shall not affect the liabilities you should bear for using this Game service before the termination of the Account, which you are still obliged to bear, including but not limited to the possible liabilities for breach of aforesaid contract, damages and performance obligations.

1.6 If you use the platform account for third-party login on other platforms, canceling this Game account will generally not affect your continued use of other platforms. However, please confirm the rules for the use of related accounts by such other platforms to avoid unnecessary losses. This platform is not responsible for related problems caused by account cancellation.
       
1.7 Other consequences (if any) arising from Account termination.

2.Before you apply or continue to apply for termination of your Account, in order to protect your Account security and related rights and interests, you should check first and ensure that the Account you apply for termination has met the following conditions in the meantime, which include but are not limited to:

2.1 The Account is legally owned and accessed by yourself and complies with the provisions on Account in the Terms of Service and relevant applicable rules.

2.2 The Account is in in safe and normal operation status: there is no risk of being blocked or stolen; there have been no banning or frozen records in the past 14 days; there have been no sensitive operations such as device replacement, password replacement, and Account switching in the past 14 days.

2.3 The in-Game property in the Account has been settled or properly handled, including but not limited to tickets, diamonds, battle points, items, subscription benefits, etc. In addition, there are no outstanding refunds, payables or orders:including but not limited to recharged diamonds, bundles, subscriptions, etc.

2.4 There are no disputes in this Account: including complaint, being complained, investigations by state agencies, arbitration, litigation, and other disputes.

2.5 Other conditions (if any) officially announced by VIZTA.

You may first try to handle the above problems by yourself. If you are unable to handle the problem or have any doubts in the process, please contact customer service for assistance.

3. Account termination process:
3.1 You may terminate your Account on the relevant function setting page according to the termination process and operation guidelines provided by official channels.

3.2 After you click Confirm to Terminate, VIZTA will review your Account and inform you of the result afterward. In order to further protect your legitimate rights and interests, we have the right to verify whether you meet the termination conditions stipulated in Article 2 hereof as appropriate, and comprehensively judge whether your Account meets the termination conditions according to the security status of your Account and your use of the relevant products and services. In order to protect your Account security and property rights, we have the right to conduct identity authentication for the termination application, so as to determine that you are the authorized user of the Account (e.g. email authentication, etc.). If it is found that the Account does not meet the termination conditions after comprehensive judgment, or if the identity authentication fails, your termination may fail, please contact customer service for assistance.
          
Even if we determine that you meet the termination conditions, it is merely a formality examination based on your commitment (i.e. your own commitment ensuring that the Account meets the above termination conditions), and you will be liable for ensuring that the Account meets the above termination conditions, and we will not bear corresponding legal liabilities for this.

3.3 After you have successfully completed the steps in Section 3.2 above, you are deemed to have successfully submitted your Account termination application to us. We will provide your Account with a cooling-off period (the Cooling-Off Period) of 30 days. During the Cooling-Off Period, we will not delete or anonymize the information related to the Account for the time being (for example, your avatar, nickname and other Account information are still visible to your friends), except as otherwise provided by laws, regulations or relevant policies.
          
In order to ensure the successful completion of termination, we strongly advice not to access the Account during the Cooling-Off Period, otherwise you will be deemed to have suspended your application to terminate this Account.

210001.m_mMessage: "The first twelve alchemists consumed the blood of "Abel the Martyr" and mastered the secret of "Rebirth." The price, however, was to experience life rooted in the cycle of "truth," with each life playing out the same."

210002.m_mMessage:
"Legend has it that when all the "Moonblessed" gather, they will be able to return to their distant homeland—The Moon.
They hold their own philosophies, be it meek or radical, all in pursuit of their dream of returning home."

210003.m_mMessage:
"They oversee Tempus and steer the course of history.
They move through the ages and transgress the boundaries of life and death."

210004.m_mMessage:
"The forebears of the great kingdoms drew strength from consuming the Divine Body and received assurances from The Church for yielding to Tempus.
Today, both have decayed into rotten curses, plaguing our realm."

210005.m_mMessage: "One of the strongest warriors chosen by the Kingdom. Guards the Divine Body sealed within the forbidden grounds.To fulfill the next periodic cycle, known as the 'future,' they willingly remain trapped between present and past."

210006.m_mMessage:
"The Oracle descended here in the form of a meteorite, which was mined heavily by the Church, leading to the fulfillment of one prophecy after another.
And so, the story begins here, right where it ended. Like a point on a circle, it loops endlessly."

210007.m_mMessage:
"Creatures unable to withstand the surge of Black Blood will transform into Blood Beasts. They vary in form and cannot be wholly vanquished.
They will become puppets of memory, needing to continuously consume fresh blood to fill the void within."

210008.m_mMessage:
"Territory of the Ganelon family, once a place where the wolves thrived.
Since the spread of the plague, no living being remains. The emotions and memories of those who once lived here have formed into a collective consciousness, lingering in the forest pine."

210009.m_mMessage: "A name long-since sealed. Only a few remember the ebb and flow of time in those repetitive twenty years.Those who don't understand the mystery of cause and effect still call it the "Ganelon Forbidden Grounds.""

210010.m_mMessage:
"The El Dorado, a grand merchant ship built with Goldland's vast inheritance, is but a gilded shell with rotten stuffing.
It has long traveled the Sea of Medimar's trade routes, with the ultimate goal of reviving a glorious civilization now under water."

210011.m_mMessage:
"Goldland intended to imprison and smuggle Blood Beasts, but instead brought upon themselves an even greater Calamity. 
Such ambition mirrors that of the Landis Family, who once attempted to harness the power of Calamity. It is hardly surprising that they met their demise at its hand."

210012.m_mMessage:
"At the crossroads between the Plane of the Living and the Other Side, phantasmal remnants of Aeon still linger. 
If destiny on the Living Plane is a preconceived notion, perhaps the Other Side, with its promise of infinite possibilities, is actual reality."

210013.m_mMessage: "Empowered by alchemy, the forces inside the Seeds of Calamity intertwined, awakening Dracula's last remaining bloodline. Can the Pure Bloodmoon, the primordial "son of the demon," truly contend with the truth of Tempus?"

210014.m_mMessage: "The holy land closely guarded by the Church conceals the ultimate secret of the world: chaos and order are merely two sides of the same coin, born from the expansion of the void."

210015.m_mMessage: "Thank you for supporting Silver and Blood! We ask that you read the following User Agreement and Privacy Policy before continuing. By tapping Confirm, you acknowledge the content of these terms. By tapping Cancel, you will be unable to proceed."

"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Bob confronts Empousa as she tends to Hati, while Van Helsing and Noah investigate the murder method."

210031.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Noah and Ami encounter rabid sailors in the cabin."

210032.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
To escape the sailors' attack, Noah and Ami head to the storage on the third deck; meanwhile, an intense conflict breaks out between Bob and Van Helsing's group."

210033.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
The suspect William's body is found hanging from the mast."

210034.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Van Helsing's group retreats to the Captain's cabin after encountering a Blood Beast."

210035.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Van Helsing examines William's body."

210036.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Hati makes her way to the lowest deck by mistake after recovering."

210037.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Noah discovers a hidden door in the storage room and reunites with Van Helsing on the third deck."

210038.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Van Helsing tracks William, who is disguised as Goldland, to the third deck."

210039.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Noah and others pursue William to the lowest deck."

210040.m_mMessage:
"Current situation aboard the El Dorado—
Noah and Van Helsing confront William on the lowest deck."
